"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Vitalik 回顾自己的十年：\\n\\n1\\\\.目标仍是“每笔交易的成本不应超过 5 美分”；\\n\\n2\\\\.曾看好比特币现金但它很难长期坚持；\\n\\n3\\\\.设想的应用几乎完全实现了（Uniswap ENS 预言机 DAO），但完全没有预料到 NFT 的爆发；\\n\\n4\\\\.曾在2015年预测以太坊会实现POS与分片（分享一个2015年的PPT截图）。\\n\\n[https://www.wu-talk.com/html/kuaixun/2022_2422.html](https://www.wu-talk.com/html/kuaixun/2022_2422.html)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5z0WiG2mPcKVYOtajYx4F.png?height=385&width=690)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641199238,\"title\":\"V神发推 回顾自己的区块链十年\"},\"digest\":\"abNmOG5J4RMsmmV3KGf4hWadNwHVaK_vCztyvEH9Q9Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9B2df5F5098Dc1DD8119a51280a73Cfd3d029155\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ahve0D1lhev53_UsL-gm7KUlODaBLOwGBDZK1rF_1J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eLAg3Zww0GMGwVJSFlPXlmsoaRJxisj6zK26wIm_-dc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"GH3HHe0twYiZ0TK4jcaRCxsHraO3nerUfmqaZUkFV5CllL-kllcHwew8qduYZgYDPydh10VNN5JVKK6bfCyzXA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xed6ce7fb2276d0fca9197c3d39a4dbd2e58e24964c4f942eaa9fbf3882ad26d46dff1ef690eb30c1b0b8b681ad371af4d150f2f8430c7f87f38cd3a3cd8fab281b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ahve0D1lhev53_UsL-gm7KUlODaBLOwGBDZK1rF_1J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eLAg3Zww0GMGwVJSFlPXlmsoaRJxisj6zK26wIm_-dc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"abNmOG5J4RMsmmV3KGf4hWadNwHVaK_vCztyvEH9Q9Q\"}"